title: Spigen Glas.tr Nano Liquid Universal Screen Protection - Clear
feature: Glas. tR Nano Liquid remains compatible with all Spigen cases
Alternative solution for devices with curved edges
Simple liquid application for crystal clarity with a bubble-free look
Nano-hydrophobic coating offers full coverage with oil/scratch resistance
description: Introducing Spigen' s Glas.tR Nano Liquid, a Silicon Dioxide (SiO2) is made to optimize screen protection without losing the 9H durability of a tempered glass. With Nano-hydrophobic technology, the liquid application adds an invisible coat that strengthens the screen by adding oil and scratch resistance. Keep the feel and look of the original screen with a layer of crystal clear defense with the Glas. tR Nano Liquid screen protector.
